divs: Sighting Detailsi was prichard road going toward 295. i was on a bridge crossing the bike trail and saw an object shoot across the sky in a bullet shape. just under the tree line i saw it stop and hover. when i saw this, there is no other way to explain it rather than saying it looked like a V shape but in the form < across the sky, and it looked like a city of lights were floating in the sky.But it was only from ONE huge ship. i talked to everyone in my family besides my dad and of course they all said i watch to much ufo hunters.... i no what i saw. i then proceeded to tell my dad about the siting and he stopped me in mid sentence of explaining the location and said "near the old halasema air strip?" and that was the perfect location for it. as far as i know that airship hasnt been used since the 80's? i contacted the local JSO (police) and said that they'll send an officer out. havent heard any other contact about it. i even called my friends that live around the area and they said havent seen a thing.
Summary: v shape when hovering cigar shape with on path, huge! still cant believe i saw this
